data.description: Here it is!! This oversized 100% BRICK ranch located on a 75 ft X 164 ft deep lot in the most desirable Fords neighborhood is ready for you. Newer central air, furnace, new dishwasher and move in clean makes this home a no brainer. Don't wait...
